      "raw_text": "PHEONlX, b. c.. April 20.-Four\nhundred employees Of the British\nColumbia Copper company at Green\nwood smelter and the Mother Lode\nand Orc Denoro mines. are on a\nstrike today following the COM\npany's refusal to grant the demand\nthat only members of the Western\nFederation of Miners be employed.\nThe strike Is the result of a vote\ntaken Saturday. The company has\nposted notice offering all men\nwork II they care to take It."
